# Code Style

- No semicolons
- No trailing commas
- Tabs for indentation, never spaces
- Single quotes for strings

```ts
// ❌
const name = "Alice";
const list = [1, 2, 3,];

// ✅
const name = 'Alice'
const list = [1, 2, 3]
```
